speaker: trump
text: Ye kya bakchodi hai? Samajh nahi aa raha yaar!  Vector database?  Kya yeh koi naya sabzi ka naam hai?

speaker: elon
text: Dekho bhai, simple hai na!  Yeh ek database hai, lekin yeh numbers aur words nahi, vectors store karta hai. Chess mein bolte hai na,  each piece has a different value and position?  Vectors bhi aise hi hain.

speaker: trump
text: Arre yaar!  Vectors?  Mere ghar ke saare vectors toh kisi aur ke paas chale gaye!  Rent nahi de rahe! Dimag kharab kar diya inhone!

speaker: elon
text: Samjha?  Yeh  AI ke liye  important hai.  Imagine,  chessboard pe ek pawn  dusre pawn se similar hai na?  Yeh database  aise hi similar vectors dhundhta hai,  lightning fast!

speaker: trump
text: Pareshaan kar diya!  Lightning fast?  Mere ghar ka bijli ka bill toh kabhi lightning fast nahi aata!  Yeh kya strategy hai?

speaker: elon
text: Logic hai na bhai!  Is article mein itni bakchodi hai,  mujhe toh  samajh hi nahi aaya.  Kya baat kar rahe ho aap log?  Sirf pareshani badhti jaa rahi hai!
